{"tid":2121252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自私泳客硬闖泳灘 拆欄毀鐵網強開水喉沖身","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T08:21:14.000Z","uid":166360,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97e78fe08b37af71e0def677303205071f578100","tid":2121252,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"【Kelly Online】自私泳客硬闖泳灘 拆欄毀鐵網強開水喉沖身<br />\n2020-07-23 14:36<br />\n<br />\n&quot;港九拯溺員工會今早在Facebook上載多張相片，有清水灣、淺水灣、荃灣麗都灣泳灘及屯門黃金泳灘等多個地方，只見有圍封水錶的鐵網被人扭到彎曲，疑有人想撬開鐵門開水。而其他相片也可見到，圍封海灘的欄杆、膠馬、封鎖線等都被人強行拆除破壞，更影到有泳客抬高腳「跨欄」躍入圍封的泳灘。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1827049/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81%E6%B3%B3%E5%AE%A2%E7%A1%AC%E9%97%96%E6%B3%B3%E7%81%98-%E6%8B%86%E6%AC%84%E6%AF%80%E9%90%B5%E7%B6%B2%E5%BC%B7%E9%96%8B%E6%B0%B4%E5%96%89%E6%B2%96%E8%BA%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1827049%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E9%2597%2596%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E7%2581%2598-%25E6%258B%2586%25E6%25AC%2584%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2596%2589%25E6%25B2%2596%25E8%25BA%25AB&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=314bf03c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1827049%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E9%2597%2596%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E7%2581%2598-%25E6%258B%2586%25E6%25AC%2584%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2596%2589%25E6%25B2%2596%25E8%25BA%25AB&h=930f61ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/182704